                    <comment id="12382094" author="olegk" created="Mon, 10 Jan 2005 03:01:10 +0000"  >Looks okay to me. The only thing missing is a test case. Would you mind&lt;br/&gt;
providing a test case for the bug or shall I take it over from here?&lt;br/&gt;
